            div.small E.g., count votes by:
            ul.tiny
              li County
              li.fragment City
              li.fragment State
              li.fragment Country
              li.fragment Zipcode? #[span Can span multiple counties 🤷]
              li.fragment Custom areas

          section
            h2 Aggregating Temporal data
            div By truncating the date
            ul
              li 2020 June 27 5:25PM
              li.fragment 2020 June 27 5:00PM
              li.fragment 2020 June 27
              li.fragment 2020 June
              li.fragment 2020 Q1
              li.fragment 2020
            div.fragment Take a look at the #[a(href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date") date object]

          section
            h2 Aggregating Temporal data
            div By extracting parts of the date
            ul
              li 2020 June 27 5:25PM
              li.fragment Week 26 of the year
              li.fragment 5:00 - 6:00 PM
              li.fragment Saturday
              li.fragment June
